content: I am a master student of artificial intelligence at the Zhejiang University CAD&CG Lab ZJULearning Group. My research include machine learning, data mining, deep learning, computer vision, operating system, and database. I have interned as a machine learning engineer in Hangzhou FABU and Google. After graduation, I will join Optiver as a system developer.
